{"tid":611470,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"以前經常講90後垃圾，不知不覺當代既00後更垃圾","createTime":"2018-03-31T04:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T08:26:09.000Z","uid":404,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"28c06101ba92753d8417b6a09cb163a8eb75afd0","tid":611470,"uid":404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"近代既00後 佢地可能係由新一代既新移民所生<br />\n<br />\n佢地對香港既過去係無認識 <br />\n<br />\n對本土不甚了解 <br />\n<br />\n以前以為我地90後真係別人口中既垃圾<br />\n<br />\n今時今日 00後更見谷底"},{"pid":"d4649c511a34593ca648c319923f49583e63dfb2","tid":611470,"uid":66158,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"長江後浪推前浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲屌尻我哋之前佔中禍中亂港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「簡體字有咩問題」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「班八九十後拾下拾下咁」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來黃之峰幫香港ban咗國民教育都係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大陸跟本唔需要赦你哋班本土香港人<br />\n<br />\n全部大陸文化已經慢慢係網絡媒體到潛移默化緊班無批判思考嘅00後<br />\n<br />\n因為阿爺知道每日150個 唔洗到2046<br />\n <br />\n香港都一定成為廣東省其中一個市"},{"pid":"ea2638e8ed11acadfb21bf0b84f2435d19277d24","tid":611470,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:13:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"554518b377ebabf0d41a048208e2476c625dafdc","tid":611470,"uid":88862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:20:00.000Z","msg":"